*kicad-doc-4.0.0_rc1 (27 Nov 2015)

  27 Nov 2015; Ian Delaney <idella4@gentoo.org> +kicad-doc-4.0.0_rc1.ebuild,
  +metadata.xml:
  4.0.0-rc1: New KiCad documentation ebuild

  KiCad extended documentation for 4.0.0-rc1, amending help
  with more details and tutorials. Upstream split the docs
  off the main source into a separate package.

  Gentoo-Bug: #564704

