  25 Jun 2016; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> kicad-doc-4.0.1.ebuild,
  kicad-doc-4.0.2.ebuild:
  QA] Various fixes to the ebuild.

  vcs-snapshot.eclass is not needed.
  Main license is || ( GPL-3+ CC-BY-3.0 ) and some files under GPL-2 only.
  Don't change LINGUAS in global scope.
  Declare local variables and fix bad assignment in src_configure.

  Remove REQUIRED_USE; fall back to a default configuration instead.
  Especially global USE_EXPAND variables like LINGUAS or L10N should not
  require per-package micro-management of flags.

  Package-Manager: portage-2.3.0

  25 Jun 2016; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> kicad-doc-4.0.1.ebuild,
  kicad-doc-4.0.2.ebuild:
